Description_lang: Abilities that activate Combo Strikes reduce the cooldown of Invoke Xuen, the White Tiger by ${$s2/-1000}.1 sec, and Xuen's damage is increased by |cFFFFFFFF${$s1}.1%|r.

description_blz.en_US: Abilities that activate Combo Strikes reduce the cooldown of Invoke Xuen, the White Tiger by 0.1 sec, and Xuen's damage is increased by 10.0%.
description_blz.es_MX: Las habilidades que activan golpes de combo reducen 0.1 s el tiempo de reutilización de Invocar a Xuen, el Tigre Blanco, y el daño de Xuen aumenta un 10.0%.
description_blz.pt_BR: Habilidades que ativam Sessão de Porrada reduzem a recarga de Evocar Xuen, o Tigre Branco, em 0,1 s, e aumentam o dano de Xuen em 10,0%.
description_blz.de_DE: Fähigkeiten, die 'Comboschläge' aktivieren, verringern die Abklingzeit von 'Xuen den Weißen Tiger beschwören' um 0,1 Sek. und Xuen verursacht 10,0% mehr Schaden.
description_blz.en_GB: Abilities that activate Combo Strikes reduce the cooldown of Invoke Xuen, the White Tiger by 0.1 sec, and Xuen's damage is increased by 10.0%.
description_blz.es_ES: Las facultades que activan Golpes de combo reducen 0,1 s el tiempo de reutilización de Invocar a Xuen, el Tigre Blanco, y el daño de Xuen aumenta un 10,0%.
description_blz.fr_FR: Les techniques qui activent Frappes combo réduisent de 0,1 s le temps de recharge d’Invocation de Xuen, le Tigre blanc, et augmentent les dégâts de Xuen de 10,0%.
description_blz.it_IT: Le abilità che attivano Sequenza Combo riducono il tempo di recupero di Invocazione: Xuen, la Tigre Bianca di 0,1 s. I danni inflitti da Xuen sono aumentati del 10,0%.
description_blz.ru_RU: Способности, активирующие "Серию ударов", сокращают время восстановления "Призыва Сюэня, Белого Тигра" на 0,1 сек. Увеличивает наносимый Сюэнем урон на 10,0%.
description_blz.ko_KR: 연계 일격을 발동시키는 능력이 백호 쉬엔의 원령의 재사용 대기시간을 0.1초만큼 감소시키고, 쉬엔의 공격력을 10.0%만큼 증가시킵니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 啟動連環打的技能可使召喚白虎雪怒的冷卻時間縮短0.1秒，並使雪怒的傷害提高10.0%。
description_blz.zh_CN: 能够触发组合拳的技能会使白虎下凡的冷却时间缩短0.1秒，并且使雪怒的伤害提高10.0%。
